The First Mac Pass Repeater Group DMR Repeater in New Mexico Sandia Crest 2 miles East of Albuquerque, NM. 10,600 Feet Elevation. 50 watt Hytera RD985 Repeater. Dual Mix with Analog, PL 131.8. Receive Antenna is Directional to the West at 10 db gain, the Transmit antenna is a Celwave PD-1151 8dBd omni pattern. Tower height is 65 feet, repeater antennas are on top. The repeater is working very, very well and no RF Noise issues on the mountain. (Lat 35.216747 Long-106.452507) On the air April 27, 2019.
